text: {'text': "Was here for a friend's wedding ceremony, and was pleasantly surprised by many things. It's right by the NUS High school, opposite Nan Hua secondary school, where I never knew a church existed here. It also reminded me of all other nice Catholic wedding ceremonies, which has a warm fuzzy feeling at the end of it all. The hour spent here was calm and peaceful. Thanks!", 'languageCode': 'en'}
